== Rescale CFG
   - The multiplier is for the œï (phi) variable
     The closer to 1.00, the stronger the ability to increase CFG scale
     The closer to 0.00, the less effect it has 
     Default value 0.7
   - https://arxiv.org/pdf/2305.08891 
     p 7, fig 6

== FreeU V2
   - FreeU: Free Lunch in Diffusion U-Net Explained 
     https://youtu.be/eFmkJ_oEW5s 
   - Value of 1.00 will have no effect
   - b (backbone) affects low-frequency features (large features)
   - s (skip) has more of an effect on higher frequency features (small features)
   - 1 & 2 = 1st pass & 2nd pass
   - https://arxiv.org/pdf/2309.11497 
     p 3, The backbone of U-Net.
     p 4, The skip connections of U-Net.
